subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Jeong Jang of South Korea shot a six-under-par 66 to take a one-stroke lead over her countrywoman Mi Hyun Kim and the rookie Brittany Lang after three rounds of the Wegmans L.P.G.A. in Pittsford, N.Y.
